Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.33,0:00:09.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在塔利比亞回歸聯合之際  美國總統進行了緊急訪問
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.99,0:00:13.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,訂立了物資援助和增加能量供給的協約
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.69,0:00:18.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然  一連串的事件全都是美國和塔利比亞策劃好的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.38,0:00:22.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而在此事件中Celestial Being被利用了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.32,0:00:24.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.67,0:00:29.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Celestial Being不過是貫徹了根除戰爭的意志
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.45,0:00:31.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而對塔利比亞展開了攻擊而已
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.17,0:00:34.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便是受到世人的憎恨
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.23,0:00:39.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要利用他們什麼的還得重新考慮才行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.21,0:00:40.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,席琳…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.35,0:00:44.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗娜公主  差不多該去各國周遊了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.49,0:00:47.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,期待著您的好消息
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.74,0:00:49.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會盡力而為的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.36,0:00:54.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了挽救阿扎提斯坦  太陽光能量是必須的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.92,0:01:01.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恕我問一句  您為何接受了這個使命
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.52,0:01:06.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還用問嗎  當然是因為只有我才能完成
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.08,0:02:44.47,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}#05  脫離極限的領域
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.75,0:02:46.88,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的天柱交通班車E603…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.08,0:02:51.07,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(250,250)}人革聯  軌道電梯  線性列車等候大廳
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.78,0:02:48.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐  你也沒必要特地來送我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.02,0:02:51.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好這邊的分公司有點事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.44,0:02:54.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了  沙慈  一定要好好學哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.11,0:02:59.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是低費用的見習旅行  這旅行費也是我付的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.58,0:03:01.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  給你造成了壓力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.53,0:03:04.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路易絲硬是要單獨房間
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.51,0:03:08.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  有錢的大小姐真是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.78,0:03:10.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.73,0:03:11.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路…路易絲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.49,0:03:14.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請放心  姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.74,0:03:18.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會好好照顧沙慈的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.72,0:03:19.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.16,0:03:22.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路易絲在我就放心了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.96,0:03:27.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙慈  別因為是旅行而太放縱哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.49,0:03:29.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要對路易絲亂來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.78,0:03:31.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼呢  姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.03,0:03:33.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的  姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.16,0:03:36.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙慈不會有這種歪腦筋的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.80,0:03:38.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.57,0:03:43.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說實話  我覺得這女孩不太適合你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.38,0:03:45.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都聽到了哦  姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.90,0:03:51.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手續辦妥了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.60,0:03:52.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出發吧  少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.84,0:03:54.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白  中校
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.53,0:04:09.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MS的…性能測試…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.42,0:04:14.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皇小姐已把任務計劃發過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.66,0:04:18.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是監視MS的性能測試
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.62,0:04:21.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根據情況  也可實施摧毀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.80,0:04:23.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得小心點  阿里路亞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.31,0:04:28.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自塔利比亞事件以來  我們被全世界都討厭了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.84,0:04:31.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感謝你的忠告
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.43,0:04:40.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎各位今天搭乘天柱交通公司班車E603
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.19,0:04:45.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本線性列車是到低軌道平台——真柱的特快
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.49,0:04:49.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到達時間是18點32分
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.99,0:04:54.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,格林威治標準時間為明天3點32分
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.38,0:04:57.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初期加速已完成
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.90,0:05:01.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從現在起  本列車將開始緩慢的減速
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.99,0:05:04.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,車廂內將構成無重力狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.46,0:05:08.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在鬆開保險帶時千萬注意
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.98,0:05:13.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太陽光發電裝置建設計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.23,0:05:22.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是人類在地球的化石原料枯竭後\N為了獲得新的能源  而於半個世紀前展開的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.79,0:05:28.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發電裝置以全長近5萬公里的軌道電梯為中心…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.99,0:05:40.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來  我還沒問過少尉你為何要志願加入超人機關呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.84,0:05:43.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並不是志願的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.51,0:05:48.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是為超兵計劃而培養出的Design Baby
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.74,0:06:03.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超兵1號由置於體內的納米機器來保持身體機能
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.99,0:06:07.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可在宇宙環境中進行長時間活動
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.84,0:06:11.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此外  通過增強各神經系統的感覺…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.43,0:06:12.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必說明了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.48,0:06:15.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是否有什麼地方不合適
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.81,0:06:19.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機關對自己的所為不覺得什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.82,0:06:21.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不覺得有什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.38,0:06:27.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了在惡劣的宇宙環境中壓制敵人  少尉的存在不可或缺
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.47,0:06:36.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  中校
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.70,0:06:39.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.32,0:06:47.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,儲藏太陽光能量的衛星通過微波通訊而向軌道電梯提供電能
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.62,0:06:52.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後通過電梯而向地面上的各地區輸送電流
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.46,0:06:56.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一天的電流供給量為1.2能量單位
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.79,0:07:06.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前  參加人類革新聯盟的35個國家由能源中部直接供給電源
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.55,0:07:07.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此外…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.33,0:07:12.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路易絲  我還在看呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.42,0:07:14.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了啦  去玩吧  去玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.09,0:07:19.90,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}人革聯  低軌道平台  真柱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.89,0:07:26.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總算到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.30,0:07:29.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.59,0:07:32.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,累了啦  被你拉著到處轉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.18,0:07:34.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真沒出息
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.54,0:07:36.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道你耐力好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.40,0:07:39.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是沙慈·克洛斯羅德和路易絲·哈萊維吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.77,0:07:40.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.09,0:07:41.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.56,0:07:45.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是負責你們見習的摩爾斯·阿斯蘭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.15,0:07:48.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎來到低軌道平台——真柱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.43,0:07:53.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙慈  你知道為什麼需要低軌道環嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.04,0:07:58.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  使磁性流體在環內流動以產生向心力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.96,0:08:01.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從而使整個平台穩定在軌道高度
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.13,0:08:02.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.26,0:08:05.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學得不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.42,0:08:07.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  沙慈  快來看看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.43,0:08:11.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要這樣  路易絲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.94,0:08:13.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能隨便去那種地方…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.69,0:08:24.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真美啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.12,0:08:27.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.08,0:08:30.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與看影像時完全不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.14,0:08:31.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.45,0:08:33.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩位小心點
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.49,0:08:36.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖是1萬千米的高度  但還有一定的重力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.49,0:08:40.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是跨出一步  那就會掉向地球哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.39,0:08:41.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.74,0:08:43.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.86,0:08:56.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙慈真笨  好好救我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.35,0:09:03.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.63,0:09:07.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這邊  中校
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.34,0:09:09.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這機體嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.95,0:09:14.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  與超兵1號的反應速度相適應的機體
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.77,0:09:19.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MSJ-06II-SP  鐵人  桃子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.92,0:09:23.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鐵人桃子  我的MS
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.33,0:09:26.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對付Gundam的王牌嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.29,0:09:42.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用完餐了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.93,0:09:43.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.76,0:09:46.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是否要什麼飲料嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.63,0:09:47.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咖啡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.85,0:09:48.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.57,0:09:50.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是旅行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.87,0:09:53.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡從高處看地球
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.19,0:09:55.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能體會你的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.07,0:09:57.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地面上太讓人煩惱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.43,0:10:00.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至還出現了Celestial Being什麼的組織
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.28,0:10:04.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很討厭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.37,0:10:08.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就要達了  在那之前請好好休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.80,0:10:18.96,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(250,250)}人革聯  低軌道平台  重力區
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.25,0:10:22.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然有重力真好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.31,0:10:23.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.63,0:10:27.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐  馬上到時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.02,0:10:29.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.18,0:10:36.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.03,0:10:37.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別東張西望
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.33,0:10:39.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱…抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.52,0:10:46.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.39,0:10:47.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了考察機體的運動性能
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.14,0:10:50.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請嘗試以最大加速度沿確定的軌道環繞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.34,0:10:52.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了  中校
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.52,0:10:57.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出發
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.99,0:11:03.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,達到最大加速
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.37,0:11:12.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在最大加速度下只和路徑偏差了0.25
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.88,0:11:14.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是超兵的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.40,0:11:19.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  她還只是個少女
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.19,0:11:23.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼感覺…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.77,0:11:29.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.34,0:11:31.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,頭…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.87,0:11:33.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.70,0:11:39.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少尉  偏離規定軌道了  怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.27,0:11:45.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中…中校  有什麼東西在刺激我的頭…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.45,0:11:54.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這頭疼是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.12,0:12:03.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該死  是哪裡來的什麼傢伙  隨便進入老子身體中的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.97,0:12:06.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.29,0:12:09.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙  要殺了你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.33,0:12:11.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要——
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.66,0:12:18.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手  少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.67,0:12:20.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要  不要啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.64,0:12:26.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.11,0:12:27.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.36,0:12:29.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少尉！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.81,0:12:36.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.04,0:12:37.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.95,0:12:40.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.93,0:12:42.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停不下來嗎  少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.42,0:12:50.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  這是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.85,0:12:52.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遇到了行星碎片嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.78,0:12:54.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手  少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.06,0:13:08.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.99,0:13:11.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路易絲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.62,0:13:13.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼搞的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.92,0:13:14.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重力…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.73,0:13:18.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰  那個傢伙是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.76,0:13:19.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  那個
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.54,0:13:21.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是重力塊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.13,0:13:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出事故了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.56,0:13:28.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是可憐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.85,0:13:29.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈里路亞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.53,0:13:32.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別多管閒事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.85,0:13:34.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈里路亞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.92,0:13:39.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們…會死嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.94,0:13:42.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要  我不想死！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.98,0:13:46.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺了我吧  阿里路亞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.79,0:13:51.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.56,0:13:57.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼搞的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.15,0:14:01.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少尉…少尉！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.60,0:14:05.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管理中心  我是謝爾蓋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.48,0:14:07.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴我重力塊的受損情況
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.11,0:14:11.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中校  根據事故發生時的緊急聯絡判斷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.83,0:14:16.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被分離開的第7重力區域裡有232名乘客
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.31,0:14:18.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救援隊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.61,0:14:20.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,預計在7分鐘後派出救援隊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.04,0:14:23.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也已經向負責守備的小分隊發出緊急出發的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.71,0:14:26.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但由於爆炸所產生的衝擊以及空氣的洩露
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.26,0:14:29.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第7重力區域的速度急速下降
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.70,0:14:34.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,14分鐘後將會落入地球引力圈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.59,0:14:35.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.03,0:14:37.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進入救援行動
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.37,0:14:38.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓回收少尉機體的部隊出動
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.14,0:14:41.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  質量那麼大的東西…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.25,0:14:42.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人命關天
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.40,0:14:52.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救援隊出發了啊  但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.02,0:14:54.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在時間上怎麼也趕不上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.93,0:14:59.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重力塊會被地球的引力牽引
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.33,0:14:59.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.85,0:15:04.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐  阿里路亞·哈普提茲姆他…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.90,0:15:05.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.05,0:15:09.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個重力塊完全脫離了空間站
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.45,0:15:12.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是說在漂流中？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.50,0:15:14.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.59,0:15:15.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救援隊馬上就來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.19,0:15:17.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,堅持到那時候吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.51,0:15:22.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有7分鐘就要到達臨界脫離區域了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.42,0:15:26.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要讓重力塊回到原本的高度
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.27,0:15:29.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有讓那個龐然大物加速才行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.60,0:15:37.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.34,0:15:44.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.05,0:15:46.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才計算了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.06,0:15:51.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個重力區域還有5分鐘就要落入地球引力圈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.54,0:15:52.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.90,0:15:53.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙…沙慈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.41,0:15:57.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開玩笑吧  只剩下5分鐘…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.55,0:16:05.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第7區域的質量太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.03,0:16:07.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光靠這台機體的推進力…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.22,0:16:12.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離到達臨界脫離區域還有200秒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.83,0:16:18.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去我的機體也要被吸入重力圈裡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.80,0:16:22.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能對這200多人見死不救嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.28,0:16:27.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙啊  你為什麼如此無情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.69,0:16:31.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個以高速接近的機體是…？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.73,0:16:34.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼到現在雷達才發現
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.99,0:16:35.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.12,0:16:40.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是Gundam嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.57,0:16:43.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿里路亞  阿里路亞·哈普提茲姆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.79,0:16:44.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.19,0:16:46.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交給你的任務呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.22,0:16:49.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可是無法明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.06,0:16:53.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙漂流者的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.27,0:16:57.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離到達臨界脫離區域還有20秒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.11,0:16:58.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kyrios！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.14,0:17:10.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.51,0:17:12.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又  又有…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.08,0:17:14.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.98,0:17:24.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維持住了…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.72,0:17:27.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  Celestial Being竟然會救人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.00,0:17:32.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後就看皇小姐了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.60,0:17:36.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王留美發出了緊急機密訊號
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.94,0:17:40.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救人…  那個孩子在做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.95,0:17:41.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.20,0:17:43.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還用說嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.09,0:17:47.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,速報  空間站事故的失蹤者名單出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.95,0:17:57.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.67,0:18:04.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使有Gundam那樣的推進力
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.13,0:18:06.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維持現狀也已經是極限了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.23,0:18:10.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  燃料用盡以後  也只能落入地球圈了…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.14,0:18:14.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽得到嗎  全員集中到中央區域
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.68,0:18:16.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個聲音  是Gundam的機師嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.45,0:18:20.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重複一遍  不想死的話  趕快集中到中央去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.76,0:18:23.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…援救行動嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.65,0:18:24.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧  路易絲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.73,0:18:28.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒時間了  快點
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.09,0:18:31.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,年輕男子的聲音…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.27,0:18:38.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  沙慈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.17,0:18:41.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定這次就沒命了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.20,0:18:43.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想現在就對你說
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.27,0:18:45.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路易絲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.13,0:18:48.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能聽到嗎  Gundam機師
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.76,0:18:52.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個東西馬上就要進入脫離極限的領域
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.52,0:18:55.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到此為止了  趕快放開
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.82,0:18:57.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼  做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.03,0:19:01.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Celestial Being是不允許失敗的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.75,0:19:02.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.01,0:19:05.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對沙慈你…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.89,0:19:07.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam Meister可不是一個人！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.47,0:19:11.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.42,0:19:14.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.51,0:19:18.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛克恩·斯托拉托斯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.52,0:19:22.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GN粒子高濃度壓縮中
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.35,0:19:29.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距填充完畢還有20  19  18  17  16…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.08,0:19:32.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發射方向的軸線上有雲擋著
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.28,0:19:34.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把它切開  刹那！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.46,0:19:38.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.56,0:19:44.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,填充完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.04,0:19:46.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進行狙擊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.15,0:19:59.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很棒的支援  皇小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.88,0:20:01.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我上去！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.71,0:20:07.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從地面狙擊那兩個重力塊讓它們分離開
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.31,0:20:11.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,減輕重量後  再把它推入安全軌道…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.86,0:20:16.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救援隊來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.03,0:20:27.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中…中校  Gundam…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.54,0:20:30.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救援行動是最優先的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.45,0:20:31.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明…明白
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.52,0:20:35.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是我  也是知道感恩的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.64,0:20:41.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,速報  全員安全獲救
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.77,0:20:50.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任務完成
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.38,0:21:02.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放棄吠陀安排的任務  優先去救人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.11,0:21:08.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  Dynames的高精度狙擊能力也向全世界暴露了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.70,0:21:11.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有必要大幅度修正本來的計劃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.69,0:21:15.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改變原來的任務  向洛克恩·斯托拉托斯下達命令的可是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.91,0:21:19.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我並不是為了幫助阿里路亞·哈普提茲姆
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.64,0:21:22.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是為了保護Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.71,0:21:26.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並不是只要適性相符合  就都能乘上Gundam的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.18,0:21:30.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又怎樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.94,0:21:39.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們差點就死了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.91,0:21:40.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路易絲…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.28,0:21:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.86,0:21:44.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.60,0:21:46.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  路易絲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.13,0:21:49.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你最後想說的…到底是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.82,0:21:54.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.58,0:22:03.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…不告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.21,0:23:36.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使在一成不變的戰場上
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.09,0:23:39.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Celestial Being也不會保持沉默
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.04,0:23:41.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,配置了新武器的Gundam們
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.08,0:23:44.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要向世界表明自己的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.65,0:23:46.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集  「七劍」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.88,0:23:48.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經再也回不來了


